# Python CLI tools installed per-user on first login via `uv tool install`.
#
# Mirrors the `pip install --user` block from arkane/post-install.sh, but uses uv
# instead of pip (honouring the "never pip, use uv" preference). Installed by the
# hummingbird-pytools.service user unit (see overlay/post_install).
#
# Format: one PyPI package (uv tool) per line.

pre-commit
tt-time-tracker
parliament
aws-policy-generator
gcalcli
posting
protonup
